## User Segments & Willingness to Pay

### Consumer Tier (Free)

**Users:** Content creators, students, music enthusiasts, gamers, fashion enthusiasts, job seekers, curious generalists

**Value Prop:** Jump on trends 48-72 hours before they peak. Learn skills before market demands them.

**Monetization:** Freemium with optional $0 (ad-supported) or $4.99/month (ad-free)

**Market Size:** 50M+ potential users globally

### Prosumer Tier ($29/month)

**Users:** Independent journalists, indie founders, freelance marketers, researchers, resellers, educators, podcasters, brand builders, startup founders, sports analysts

**Value Prop:** Break stories before mainstream. Validate ideas against emerging demand. Find topics before everyone covers them.

**Willingness to Pay:** $29-99/month (proven by Substack, Patreon, Notion Pro adoption)

**Market Size:** 2-5M potential users globally

**Annual Revenue Potential:** $870M - $1.8B at 50% penetration

### B2B Tier ($299-$2,000/month)

**Users:** Marketing teams, product teams, VC firms, brand agencies, news organizations, hedge funds, government, NGOs, e-commerce companies, record labels

**Value Prop:** Cultural intelligence for campaign timing. Demand signals for roadmap decisions. Sector trend intelligence for deal flow.

**Willingness to Pay:** $299-$2,000/month (proven by Semrush, HubSpot, Slack adoption)

**Market Size:** 50K-200K potential teams globally

**Annual Revenue Potential:** $1.8B - $4.8B at 30% penetration

### API Tier (Usage-Based)

**Users:** Developers, enterprise data teams, academic researchers, aggregators

**Value Prop:** Programmatic access to signal data. Custom integrations. Resell signals in industry-specific products.

**Willingness to Pay:** $0.001-$0.01 per signal + $500-$5,000/month base

**Market Size:** 10K-50K potential customers globally

**Annual Revenue Potential:** $500M - $2B at 20% penetration

