## Risk Analysis & Mitigation

### Technical Risks

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|---|
| MiroFish simulation accuracy | Medium | High | Continuous validation against real-world trends. Publish accuracy metrics. |
| Multi-source scraping reliability | Medium | High | Redundant scrapers. Fallback to manual curation. |
| Real-time processing at scale | Low | High | Ray distributed computing. Kubernetes autoscaling. Load testing. |

### Market Risks

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|---|
| Google releases predictive trends | Medium | High | Move upmarket to B2B. Focus on simulation depth. |
| Platforms block scrapers | Medium | Medium | Negotiate data partnerships. Use official APIs where available. |
| User adoption slower than expected | Low | Medium | Freemium model ensures user acquisition. Focus on prosumer conversion. |

### Competitive Risks

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|---|
| Existing players add simulation | Medium | Medium | Build moat through community + accuracy. Open-source framework. |
| New entrants with better UX | Low | Medium | Focus on design excellence. Iterate rapidly. |

